    "id": "clms_wsi_sar-wet-snow_europe_utm_60m_daily_v2",
    "title": "SAR Wet Snow 2016-present (raster 60 m), Europe, daily",
    "description": "The SAR Wet Snow (SWS) product is generated in near real-time for selected high mountain areas at European scale based on C-band Synthetic Aperture Radar satellite data from the Sentinel-1 constellation. The product provides the wet snow extent for high mountain areas with a spatial resolution of 60 m x 60 m.",
